                <h1>How to Add a White Background to Any Photo</h1>
                <p>To add a white background to a photo, use editing software like Photoshop or online tools like Canva. Open the image and select the subject using the lasso or magic wand tool. Invert the selection, then delete the current background. Finally, create a new layer filled with white to set as the background. Save your edited photo!</p>
